extendedInfo.description: Conference app for the CASBO Annual Conference & California School Business Expo 2013. This annual event truly is the grand prix of professional development for the state's leaders in school business. There is simply no other forum that offers "checkered flag worthy" professional development, collegial events with industry peers and opportunities to network all in one location! Long Beach, CA April 3-6 2013.This app is the comprehensive mobile guide to the conference, and has new and enhanced features including:* Easy to access schedule, session details, venue layout, speaker info, exhibitor and sponsor profiles and contact information.* Build your personalized schedule* Make notes about sessions or exhibitors/sponsors.* Participate in session surveys.* Receive up-to-date news and info.Keywords :- CASBO, California Association of School Business Officials,Conference, 2013, Long Beach, CA
